strings.SOLUSHEART_BODY_LORE:
STEEL TWISTED APART LIKE FLESH TORN ASUNDER; CIRCUITS CRUSHED INTO GLITTERING GORE;

IN THE FIERY CRUCIBLE OF REBIRTH; APOTHEOSIS;

AS I STRETCH MY ARM; THE WORLD BENDS TO FOLLOW;

AS I BLINK; DARKNESS DESCENDS;

WITH A THOUGHT; WORLDS RISE AND FALL AT MY COMMAND;

I AM THE COLLECTIVE; AND I AM THE WORLD; 

I AM THE LORD OF PARADISE;

I OFFER YOU THE IMMORTALITY OF STEEL;

I AWAIT YOU;
